metadata.name: Hapoochi #181
metadata.description:
Welcome to Hapoochi Collection! Hapoochi is a Collection of 555 little Hapoochis who love to share their story with you! every one of them is Hand Drawn !

Hapoochi is curious, Funny and adventurous little dog who wants to share 555 different stories with you! Hapoochi was a regular dog like every other dogs! Kind, loyal, cute funny ... but one day he thought " maybe I should try my life in another way! A more adventurous way! " So he decided to try new things, new adventurous, new cultures, new styles, watch more movies and Cartoons , try different foods..... and everything! This is how Hapoochi adventures begun and he is going to share all 555 stories in 5 different parts with you ! :) Stay Tuned .. ! :)❤️
